---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  seo={{
    title: "About Praveen — IT Ops Lead, AI Automation Builder",
    description: "I'm an IT Operations Lead who documents real AI experiments using DeepSeek and OpenCode. This site shares what actually works and what breaks in production.",
  }}
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-16">

    <!-- Hero section -->
    <div class="mb-16 grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] md:items-start">
      <div>
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-brand-200 bg-brand-50 px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-700 dark:border-brand-800/40 dark:bg-brand-900/20 dark:text-brand-400 mb-6">
          Building in Public
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text dark:text-text-dark mb-4">
          Hi, I'm Praveen.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted dark:text-text-dark-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I'm an IT Operations Lead — not a software engineer. I use AI tools (primarily DeepSeek and OpenCode) to build automation scripts, data pipelines, and IT tools that I would never write from scratch.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted dark:text-text-dark-muted leading-relaxed">
          This site is where I document every experiment honestly: what I asked the AI, what it produced, where it failed, and how I fixed it.
          No fake expertise. No polished "how-to" fluff that skips the hard parts.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 shrink-0">
        <a href="https://x.com/praveenwithapen" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-border px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-text-muted transition-all hover:border-brand-600 hover:text-brand-600 dark:border-border-dark dark:text-text-dark-muted dark:hover:border-brand-400 dark:hover:text-brand-400">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
          @praveenwithapen
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/praveen-kumar-says/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-border px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-text-muted transition-all hover:border-brand-600 hover:text-brand-600 dark:border-border-dark dark:text-text-dark-muted dark:hover:border-brand-400 dark:hover:text-brand-400">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
          LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Divider -->
    <hr class="border-border dark:border-border-dark mb-16" />

    <!-- Why this site exists -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text dark:text-text-dark mb-4">Why this site exists</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-text-muted dark:text-text-dark-muted leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Most technology content falls into two camps: overly technical guides that assume you know the jargon, and surface-level listicles that leave you with nothing working. 
        </p>
        <p>
          I built PraveenTechWorld to bridge that gap. Every article here comes from a real situation I faced — a task I needed to automate, a Windows error that blocked my work, a script that failed in production. I document the full journey, not just the happy path.
        </p>
        <p>
          The site runs on an AI-assisted content pipeline that I built and operate myself. The automation finds topics, generates first drafts, and handles publishing — but every piece goes through real judgment before it goes live.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- What I cover -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text dark:text-text-dark mb-6">What I cover</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        {[
          { icon: "⚙️", title: "AI Automation Scripts", desc: "Python scripts, CLI tools, and pipelines built with DeepSeek prompting." },
          { icon: "🖥️", title: "IT Operations", desc: "Real sysadmin tasks: server health checks, certificate renewal, log monitoring." },
          { icon: "🛠️", title: "Windows Troubleshooting", desc: "Step-by-step fixes for Windows 11 errors, update failures, and performance issues." },
          { icon: "🌐", title: "Website Setup & SEO", desc: "How to index your site, fix Search Console issues, and grow organic traffic." },
          { icon: "☁️", title: "Hosting & Infrastructure", desc: "Practical guides for Vercel, Astro, Cloudflare, and static site deployment." },
          { icon: "📢", title: "Build in Public", desc: "What I'm building, what broke, what I learned — documented in real time." },
        ].map(item => (
          <div class="flex gap-4 rounded-2xl border border-border dark:border-border-dark p-5 transition-all hover:border-brand-200 dark:hover:border-brand-800/50">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">{item.icon}</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-text dark:text-text-dark mb-1">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-muted dark:text-text-dark-muted">{item.desc}</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Philosophy -->
    <section class="mb-16 rounded-2xl border border-brand-200 bg-brand-50/50 dark:border-brand-800/30 dark:bg-brand-900/10 p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text dark:text-text-dark mb-4">My content philosophy</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-text-muted dark:text-text-dark-muted">
        {[
          "Every guide comes from something I actually needed to solve",
          "I show the AI prompts I used and where the AI got it wrong",
          "I don't chase trends — I write when I have something real to say",
          "Fixes are tested before I write them up",
          "I'd rather write one honest article than ten padding articles",
        ].map(item => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 shrink-0 text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
            <span class="text-sm">{item}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text dark:text-text-dark mb-4">Start reading</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-brand-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all hover:bg-brand-700 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-600/20">
          Browse all articles
        </a>
        <a href="/guides" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-border px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-text transition-all hover:border-brand-600 hover:text-brand-600 dark:border-border-dark dark:text-text-dark dark:hover:border-brand-400 dark:hover:text-brand-400">
          View guides by topic
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-border px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-text transition-all hover:border-brand-600 hover:text-brand-600 dark:border-border-dark dark:text-text-dark dark:hover:border-brand-400 dark:hover:text-brand-400">
          Get in touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
